    • isApplicable

      protected boolean isApplicable(String tableName)
      Check if the table is applicable for opening. Override this method to include criteria that the table must meet or to alter the specified table name
      Parameters:
      tableName - The raw value from the table cell specified as the table name column in the openTables() method
      Returns:
      True if the table should be added to the list of ones to open
